my_palette <- colorRampPalette(c("mintcream", "lightskyblue", "navyblue"))(n = 299)
lmat = rbind(c(0, 3),
             c(2, 1), 
             c(0, 4))
lwid = c(1,1.5)
lhei = c(0.4,1.5,0.68)
title <- "K562seq 100v100 Rand Seed 4"
gmtk3data1 <- read.csv("/scratch/mordor/hoffmangroup/wxu/data/2018-06-01_Segway_Run_3/gmtk_parameters/gmtk_parameters.stats.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",", row.names = 1)
gmtk4data1 <- read.csv("/scratch/mordor/hoffmangroup/wxu/data/2018-06-06_Segway_Run_4/gmtk_parameters/gmtk_parameters.stats.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",", row.names = 1)
gmtk4data1 <- gmtk4data1[names(gmtk3data1)]
labelmap <- read.csv("/scratch/mordor/hoffmangroup/wxu/data/2018-06-19_Segway_Analysis/seg34r1/overlap-direct/label_map.tab", sep="\t", skip=2, header=FALSE)
ordered.map <- labelmap[order(labelmap$V1), ]
reorderindex <- (ordered.map$V2 + 1)
reordered.gmtk3data1 <- gmtk3data1[reorderindex, ]
gmtk3data1 <- reordered.gmtk3data1
transpose1 <- t(data.matrix(gmtk3data1))
transpose2 <- t(data.matrix(gmtk4data1))
# par(mfrow=c(2,1))
heatmap.2(transpose1, margins =c(5,10), dendrogram='none', Rowv = FALSE, Colv = FALSE, ylab = 'Protein Marks', xlab = 'Labels', main = title, col = my_palette, trace="none", density.info="none", lmat=lmat, lwid=lwid, lhei=lhei)

title <- "K562seq 100v100 Rand Seed 23"
heatmap.2(transpose2, margins =c(5,10), dendrogram='none', Rowv = FALSE, Colv = FALSE, ylab = 'Protein Marks', xlab = 'Labels', main = title, col = my_palette, trace="none", density.info="none", lmat=lmat, lwid=lwid, lhei=lhei)

title <- "Deg Base Overlap: K562seq 100v100"
overlap <- read.csv("/scratch/mordor/hoffmangroup/wxu/data/2018-06-19_Segway_Analysis/seg34r1/overlap-direct/overlap.tab", sep="\t", skip=1, header=TRUE)
label <- overlap[,1]
lastcolindex <- ncol(overlap)
none <- overlap[,lastcolindex-1]
overlap <- as.matrix(overlap[,-c(1, lastcolindex)])
selection <- overlap[,1:(lastcolindex-3)]
colnames(selection) <- label
selection <- cbind(selection, none)
rownames(selection) <- label
overlap <- selection
overheatmap <- heatmap.2(overlap, margins =c(5,5), dendrogram='none', Rowv = FALSE, Colv = FALSE, ylab = 'Run 1 Labels', xlab = 'Run 2 Labels', main = title, col = my_palette, trace="none", density.info="none", lmat = lmat, lwid = lwid, lhei = lhei)

edgelist <- read.csv("/scratch/mordor/hoffmangroup/wxu/data/2018-06-19_Segway_Analysis/seg34r1/overlap-direct/label_map.tab", sep="\t", skip=2, header=FALSE)
edgelist$V1 <- paste("A", edgelist$V1, sep="")
edgelist$V2 <- paste("B", edgelist$V2, sep="")
graph <- graph.data.frame(edgelist)
V(graph)$type <- V(graph)$name %in% edgelist[,1]
V(graph)$color <- ifelse(V(graph)$type, "lightblue", "salmon")
V(graph)$shape <- ifelse(V(graph)$type, "circle", "square")
E(graph)$color <- "lightgray"
V(graph)$label.cex <- 1
V(graph)$frame.color <-  "gray"
V(graph)$size <- 17
l <- layout.bipartite(graph)
plot(graph, layout = l[, c(2,1)])
